meta.name: Hot Bench
meta.description: Three judges argue the merits of a case among themselves and render a verdict.

videos.title: Service Dog Tearjerker
videos.overview: Small-claim court cases are heard by 3 judges who must then work together to determine the verdict. In the series opener, a custody dispute is settled between the owner of a grief therapy dog and a couple who bonded with it during its time of service.

videos.title: Turn Lane Collision!; Tiny Toilet Turmoil
videos.overview: A motorist claims to be in the middle of renewing their insurance when they were involved in an accident. Also: a dispute over a home renovation.

videos.title: Beauty School Hazing?
videos.overview: A dispute between a teacher and a student of a beauty school is settled.

videos.title: Mansion Madness; Firefighter Hero Sued by Ex
videos.overview: A woman is questioned over her decision to pay for the upkeep of a mansion. Later, ex-lovers argue over the repayment of a loan.

videos.title: Devastated Daddy at Baby Girl's Party; Pit Bull vs. Chihuahua!
videos.overview: A father claims emotional distress after an entertainer doesn't show up at his daughter's party. Also: A dog owner defends their pit bull after an alleged attack on a Chihuahua.

videos.title: Kidnapping and Abuse Claims; Pimp Mobile for an 11-Year-Old?
videos.overview: Allegations of child abuse and kidnap are discussed in court between a divorced couple. Later, a botched custom bike design is disputed.

videos.title: Marijuana Test-Drive Drama; Player Hater Vandalism!
videos.overview: A teen is accused of using illegal drugs during a test drive. Also, a woman is accused of vandalizing her lover's car.

videos.title: The Very Odd Couple; Stolen Skateboard Ethics
videos.overview: A man seeks reparations after his property is damaged by a boarder. Also: A missing skateboard causes contention between friends.

videos.title: Africa Trip Fallout; When Bed Bugs Bite!
videos.overview: Disputes are raised over a trip to Africa. Later, a woman accuses her roommate of a bedbug infestation.

videos.title: BB Gun and Paternity Test; Three-Car Pile-Up!
videos.overview: An incident a loaded BB gun leads to a paternity test. Also: a dispute over a traffic collision is discussed.

videos.title: Racial Slurs and Bigotry; Homeless Widow Woes
videos.overview: A man is accused of resorting to racial slurs and threats in an attempt to get his ex-business partner to pay his share of an $8000 investment in a Cadillac Escalade. Later, a homeless widow takes a man to court for wrecking her car, but he insists that the crash was her fault.

videos.title: Female Boxer vs. Trainer
videos.overview: A woman who overcame health issues to pursue her dream of becoming a pro boxer takes her ex-trainer to court for loss of income and accuses him of breaking fight contracts.

videos.title: Murder Tears Family Apart
videos.overview: A widow who became a victims' advocate accuses her own son of assaulting her during a fight over their family home.

videos.title: Self-Made Landlord After Murder!; White Picket Fence Wipeout!
videos.overview: A landlord who became an alleged murder suspect vs. a tenant who started renting apartments in his absence. Also: A man accuses an uninsured motorist of completely destroying his fence, but she claims she didn't cause that much damage.

videos.title: Illegal Scooter Rams Mustang; Doggie Haircut Disaster
videos.overview: Photo evidence of skid marks seems to contradict a woman's version of an accident involving her unregistered, uninsured scooter and a Ford Mustang. Also: A groomer is accused of dislocating a dog's hip during a haircut.

videos.title: Workplace Romance Drama; Punched and Maced!
videos.overview: Former lovers who started dating at work find themselves in court, fighting over alleged cheating and money. Later, a couple whose relationship came to a bitter end argue over an Xbox.

videos.title: Love for Sale?; Online Gambling Loans?
videos.overview: A woman claims to have been loaned money from a man she met on the Internet. Later, a woman accuses her ex-boyfriend of running up charges on her credit card.

videos.title: Grandmother Mayhem; Medical Marijuana Delivery
videos.overview: A woman sues the father of her grandson for after her home is raided by police. Later, ex-lovers fight over money and marijuana paraphernalia.

videos.title: Gang-Related Threats
videos.overview: Illegal gang activity causes a lease dispute between a renter and her landlord.

videos.title: Rock Throwing and Harassment!; Ex-Lovers Disinterest Rate
videos.overview: A child is accused of throwing a rock at a rental car. Later, a dispute is caused over a high-interest loan.

videos.title: DUI With a Child in the Car
videos.overview: A call to the police is the cause for a dispute between a couple.

videos.title: Pitbull vs. Chihuahua; Love and Liability
videos.overview: A woman attempts to find the party responsible for a savage attack on her dog which, she claims, traumatized her children; a couple quarrel over a vehicle loan.

videos.title: Dating, Damage and Drama; Live-In Lizard?
videos.overview: A car repossession is disputed between ex-lovers; A renter brings a lizard and an roommate into his place against the wishes of his landlord.

videos.title: Tweener Instagram Fashion Fail; Hair Salon Drama

videos.title: Gossip Traded for Cash; Taunting an Ex-Lover
videos.overview: A man claims to have been paid to inform on the whereabouts of a woman's ex-lover; a man is being sued after returning a car damaged to its owner.

videos.title: Exploding Car; Anti-Bullying Business
videos.overview: A mechanic is sued after a car blows up on the highway; a dispute arises over screen printer services for an anti-bullying organization.

videos.title: A Dog's Confession?; Flat-Screen Friendship Fiasco
videos.overview: Neighbors contend over vet bills after a beagle is injured; ex-friends dispute a cellphone bill and the ownership of a flat screen t.v.

videos.title: Euthanized Dogs
videos.overview: A woman claims her sheep were attacked by her neighbors dogs.

videos.title: Innocent Man Serving Life Sentence?
videos.overview: A woman sues a private investigator after her son is sent to prison.

videos.title: Music Video Mayhem; Ex-Lover Computer Thief?
videos.overview: A music manager and film director sue one another over the production quality of a music video; a woman accuses her ex of stealing her computer.

videos.title: Forgery and Fighting; Pregnant and Moving!
videos.overview: A woman is accused of forging checks and pawning her ex-boyfriend's chainsaw; A landlord and tenant disagree over an email.

videos.title: Dog Eats Marijuana Candy!; Cupcake Crisis
videos.overview: A dog eats chocolate filled with marijuana and the owner sues her roommates for vet expenses; A woman claims the cupcakes she ordered for her child's birthday were late and refuses the baker payment.

videos.title: Disgusting Clean-Up; Tornado Debris Disaster
videos.overview: A woman sues for payment after having to clean up her tenant's dirty apartment; A woman claims to be assaulted by her neighbor after tornado leaves debris on her sidewalk.

videos.overview: A woman is accused of stealing water from her landlord; A couple argue over the ownership of an Xbox.
